metadata.name: You know me
metadata.description:
People in emotionless moments, transformed into spaces full of contrast, tension and contradictions.

It's 6:44 p.m., the day's job is done and she waits emotionlessly at the train track. exhausted and marked by the day, but deep inside the desire for escape, adventure and a new start. 

Jan Baumgartner , jnbmgrtnr
02.03.2022
